      "content": {
        "blocks": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "56ap8",
            "text": "当你发送一份老文档的图片或者PDF 给 OpenClaw 的时候，一不小心 token量就刷刷往上涨。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "dces0",
            "text": "为什么呢？",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "3oe2j",
            "text": "官方内置一些 PDF 和图片的工具都是使用大模型的能力。处理一两页还行，但是处理起大批量文件的话，价格就过于昂贵了。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "524k8",
            "text": "但是我们这个世界很多信息其实还是没有数字化的，比如说发票，合同，名片。假如不将这些信息数字化提供给 AI，AI 在公司业务中的落地几乎是不可能的。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "a8a3d",
            "text": "AI 连合同都看不到，那么如何给你判断合同中的条款是否符合你的利益呢？",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 18,
                "offset": 12,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "4v67h",
            "text": "所以，OpenClaw 急需精确，价格便宜的 OCR 方案。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "enmtv",
            "text": "文心衍生模型PaddleOCR文档解析能力基于文心大模型体系训练，已上线ClawHub，Agent 工作流中可直接调用文档解析能力，刚好能提供一个完美的解决方案",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 6,
                "offset": 34,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "sirq",
            "text": "相比昂贵的大模型视觉方案，PaddleOCR 提供了每天 1w 页的免费解析页数，而且还能申请更多。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [
              {
                "key": 0,
                "length": 1,
                "offset": 0
              }
            ],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "22lbp",
            "text": " ",
            "type": "atomic"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "77s0i",
            "text": "今天就手把手带大家快速白嫖这个福利。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "95klr",
            "text": "安装PaddleOCR Skill",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {
              "urls": [
                {
                  "fromIndex": 7,
                  "text": "https://clawhub.ai/Bobholamovic/paddleocr-doc-parsing",
                  "toIndex": 60
                }
              ]
            },
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "bnfud",
            "text": "输入下面网址：https://clawhub.ai/Bobholamovic/paddleocr-doc-parsing，我们就能看到PaddleOCR Skill。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [
              {
                "key": 1,
                "length": 1,
                "offset": 0
              }
            ],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "adukh",
            "text": " ",
            "type": "atomic"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "7bhmp",
            "text": "你以为我们需要乖乖下载安装，但是在 Agent 时代，一句话就能安装大部分东西。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "cm8p1",
            "text": "输入下面文字",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [
              {
                "key": 2,
                "length": 1,
                "offset": 0
              }
            ],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "ctm8v",
            "text": " ",
            "type": "atomic"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "7aomd",
            "text": "现在问题是，去哪里获取上面缺失的两个地址和密钥呢！！",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "91mi1",
            "text": "获取配置",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "302js",
            "text": "首先我们申请 API：",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {
              "urls": [
                {
                  "fromIndex": 5,
                  "text": "https://aistudio.baidu.com/paddleocr",
                  "toIndex": 41
                }
              ]
            },
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "au5ng",
            "text": "输入网址：https://aistudio.baidu.com/paddleocr",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [
              {
                "key": 3,
                "length": 1,
                "offset": 0
              }
            ],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "1qagb",
            "text": " ",
