            "type": "atomic"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "7hrit",
            "text": "将这些填入，上面的模板，输入到 OpenClaw 的对话框内，即可完成安装。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "2e2vl",
            "text": "但是我们大部分平时在外跑业务都是不用电脑的，下面演示如何在手机中实现名片的数字化，保存和记录",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "fe55i",
            "text": "实际案例",
            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "8h3ui",
            "text": "直接在手机上将日常业务中拍摄的图片发给 OpenClaw，要求其用 PaddleOCR 识别",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [
              {
                "key": 6,
                "length": 1,
                "offset": 0
              }
            ],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
