            "type": "header-two"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "5se6t",
            "text": "OpenClaw 将会成为操作系统时代的 Linux 系统，未来将会是 Agent 与人协同的时代。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "ff6qu",
            "text": "各个企业要拥抱 Agent，就必须将数据传递给 AI，让 AI 自动处理。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [],
            "key": "c0r6l",
            "text": "因此 OCR 作为将文档数字化的重要手段，会变得越来越不可或缺。",
            "type": "unstyled"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "entityRanges": [],
            "inlineStyleRanges": [
              {
                "length": 81,
                "offset": 0,
                "style": "Bold"
              }
            ],
            "key": "54h0h",
